{"tid":2489357,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"港台：美軍撤出阿富汗後　塔利班勢力或增大","createTime":"2021-04-15T01:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T02:12:01.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"22312429698ce07775c5adb044c3b9097e4cc1b8","tid":2489357,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T01:56:00.000Z","msg":"美軍梗係唔好走，唔係點係台海起戰端？<br />\n<br />\n美國總統拜登表示，美國將於5月1日展開從阿富汗撤軍的最後階段，預料9月11日前可以完成。<br />\n<br />\n拜登政府計劃從阿富汗撤走所有駐軍，比前總統特朗普任內訂出的撤軍時間表、即是下月一日來得較遲。<br />\n<br />\n有白宮高級官員透露，華府認為軍事行動不能解決阿富汗內政與軍事衝突，未來將集中以外交方式，支持當地的和平進程。<br />\n<br />\n有分析認為，<strong>拜登的決定或會助長當地塔利班勢力</strong>，而塔利班與阿富汗政府在美軍撤走前達成權力共享的機會亦不大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585856-20210415.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585856-20210415.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sOrkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=e8dfdb92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585856-20210415.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d26f32eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585856-20210415.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"1cbc0a5386610484919c4942f44baf4f0dfbd395","tid":2489357,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T01:58:12.000Z","msg":"好撚有用嘅分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/crystalball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/crystalball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf91530bc95d97657d75072fbe938e53e0bc8efd","tid":2489357,"uid":40267,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T01:58:27.000Z","msg":"明知蘇聯死喺哥度仲on9到自己踩隻腳落去<br />\n20年洗左幾萬億死左幾千人得個桔<br />\n布狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1b426e4d7abf5303df0720bc346b5135b0ccef","tid":2489357,"uid":40267,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-